&lt;p&gt;Would you try building and using git master, or, use a snapshot build and see if it helps? &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Snapshot builds are here: &lt;a href=&quot;https://repository.apache.org/content/repositories/snapshots/org/apache/commons/commons-imaging/1.0-SNAPSHOT/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://repository.apache.org/content/repositories/snapshots/org/apache/commons/commons-imaging/1.0-SNAPSHOT/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17741211" author="akhoury" created="Fri, 7 Jul 2023 22:54:44 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=ggregory&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;ggregory&quot;&gt;ggregory&lt;/a&gt;, yes I tested against master as well and the same issue occurs.&#160;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, I was able to fix the issue using this change &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/andrewmkhoury/commons-imaging/commit/d4a5f6a039e8ccf232750d5427f88638162db3f1&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
readFile(byteSource, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;); &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;// instead of &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;false&lt;/span&gt; to skip storing the imageData which isn&apos;t required &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;for&lt;/span&gt; getMetadata and getImageInfo&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is my updated test code I used to test the issue against git master:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/andrewmkhoury/commons-imaging-gif-test/tree/IMAGING-355&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/andrewmkhoury/commons-imaging-gif-test/tree/IMAGING-355&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

